---
description: No attribution footers in git commits
alwaysApply: true
---

# Commit messages

Never add any of the following to commit messages (subject or body):

- `Made-with:` or `made-with` (or any variant)
- `Co-authored-by:` unless the human author explicitly asks for a co-author
- Similar tool- or assistant-attribution trailers

Use only the human-written summary and body the author wants on GitHub.
